description: Welcome to Pixel Hares! A unique pixel-art collection of 8888 hand-drawn Hares with a wide variety of carefully curated traits on a 32 x 32 artboard. Each Hare is a masterpiece handcrafted with passion, love and creativity. With around 300 meticulously drawn traits, these NFTs are the epitome of originality and curation. Get ready to embark on a journey through a whimsical world where pixelated hares come to life with vibrant colors and breathtaking creativity!
name: Pixel Hares
